Package application

Class Ingredient

java.lang.Object
application.Ingredient
public class Ingredient
extends java.lang.Object
Ingredient is a Java class representing an Ingredient object with a name, amount, unit of measurement, and number of calories. Contains methods for getting and setting all data fields.
Author:
Reed Olm - avr414 - UTSA CS 3443 - CookingCompanion 2021
